flowchart TD
    A[Customer initiates payment] --> B{Payment Method}
    B -->|Card| C[Tokenize card data]
    B -->|Bank Transfer| D[ACH / SEPA / EFT]
    B -->|Digital Wallet| E[Apple Pay / Google Pay]
    
    C --> F[Send to Payment Gateway]
    D --> F
    E --> F

    F --> G{3D Secure Required?}
    G -->|Yes| H[Redirect to 3DS challenge]
    H --> I{Customer authenticated?}
    I -->|Yes| J[Authorization request]
    I -->|No| K[❌ Payment failed]
    G -->|No| J

    J --> L[Payment Gateway → Processor]
    L --> M[Processor → Card Network]
    M --> N[Card Network → Issuing Bank]

    N --> O{Issuer decision}
    O -->|Approved| P[✅ Authorization hold placed]
    O -->|Declined| K

    P --> Q{Capture method}
    Q -->|Immediate| R[Auto-capture]
    Q -->|Manual| S[Merchant captures later]
    S --> R

    R --> T[Settlement - 1 to 3 business days]
    T --> U[Funds transferred to Acquirer]
    U --> V[Acquirer deposits to Merchant]
    V --> W[💰 Merchant receives payout]

    style A fill:#4A90D9,color:#fff
    style K fill:#D0021B,color:#fff
    style P fill:#7ED321,color:#fff
    style W fill:#7ED321,color:#fff
